Package ohos.data.search.schema

Class EventItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.data.search.model.IndexData
      • ohos.data.search.schema.Schema<EventItem>
        • ohos.data.search.schema.EventItem

  • public final class EventItem
extends Schema<EventItem>
    Represents the index schema for event items.

    This schema is used to create indexes for event items. It supports index fields startDate, endDate, location, longitude, latitude, and all the fields in CommonItem. Among these fields, identifier is mandatory and can be set via the CommonItem#setIdentifier(String) method.

    Since:
    5
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Data#DATA_SEARCH
